title: CNE70196 High Quality Black DisplayPort Male to HDMI Cable Male 6ft/2M
description: C&E; display port to hdmi cable provides a simple solution for connecting a display port video source (e.g. Display port video cards, etc.) To an hdmi-enabled video display, eliminating the expense of having to upgrade your display for display port compatibility.
